name: Concept: Panty line and crotch line
description:
Caution: This LoRA is for REAListic!

It is possible to generate an animated tone, but the probability of success is reduced!

-Recommended setting-

Weights as appropriate.

Recommended checkpoint: BasilMix (https://huggingface.co/nuigurumi/basil_mix/tree/main)

Other checkpoints will work, but may not give the desired results.

Resolution recommendation : Around 500-750.

Steps : 25~30

CGF : 7.5.

Sampler : DPM++ SDE Karras.

Recommended prompt : p line, pantylines, from below, facing away, ...etc

("From below" can be changed to "from behind".)

(If you specify "jeans" or "black pants," the lines will be unnatural or difficult to see. (The safest type of pants are "beige", "slacks".)

Try adding "bent over" or "walking".)
